## üîß Troubleshooting

### Audio Issues (Voice Interface)
**Problem:** "No module named 'pyaudio'"

**Solution:**
1. Download PyAudio wheel: https://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/#pyaudio
2. Install: `pip install PyAudio‚Äë0.2.14‚Äëcp312‚Äëcp312‚Äëwin_amd64.whl`

### TensorFlow GPU Issues
**Problem:** TensorFlow not using GPU

**Solution:**
```powershell
# Install CUDA-enabled TensorFlow
pip uninstall tensorflow
pip install tensorflow[and-cuda]

# Verify GPU
python -c "import tensorflow as tf; logging.info(tf.config.list_physical_devices('GPU'))"
```

### Port Already in Use
**Problem:** "Address already in use: 8765"

**Solution:**
```powershell
# Find process using port
netstat -ano | findstr :8765

# Kill process
taskkill /PID <PID> /F

# Or change port in chimera_autarch.py
```

### Permission Errors
**Problem:** "Access denied" when running scripts

**Solution:**
```powershell
# Enable script execution
Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser

# Or run PowerShell as Administrator
```

### SSL Certificate Errors (Cloud APIs)
**Problem:** SSL verification fails

**Solution:**
```powershell
# Update certificates
pip install --upgrade certifi

# Or temporarily disable SSL verification (NOT recommended for production)
$env:PYTHONHTTPSVERIFY=0
```

